                        Quota for the minke whale hunt in 2010
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[05.12.2009]</p>
                <p>The Minister of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs has set a quota of 1286 animals for the minke whale hunt in 2010.</p>
                
                
