            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fkd/Press-Centre/Press-releases/2009/overfishing-reduced-by-84.html?id=563627" title="">
                        Overfishing reduced by 84%
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[28.05.2009]</p>
                <p>“Once again, overfishing of cod in the Barents Sea has been substantially reduced in 2008. This means that unreported fishing has been reduced by as much as 84% from 2005 to 2008 and that resources to the value of 1.1 billion kroner are now benefiting the coastal communities,” says Minister of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs Helga Pedersen.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
