            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fkd/Press-Centre/Press-releases/2008/quota-agreement-between-norway-and-the-e.html?id=538889" title="">
                        Quota agreement between Norway and the EU for 2009
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[10.12.2008]</p>
                <p>Norway and the EU have concluded a bilateral fisheries agreement for 2009. For both parties discard of fish has been the main issue during this year’s negotiations. Norway and EU have agreed on a number of measures directed at the reduction of discard.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
