                        Quota agreement between Norway and the EU for 2008
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Assistant Director General Ann Kristin Westberg,  tel.  +47 916 95 372</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[26.11.2007]</p>
                <p>Norway and the EU have concluded a bilateral fisheries agreement for 2008. The parties have also come to an agreement on fishing in the Skagerrak for next year. </p>
                
                
