                    <a href="/en/dep/fkd/Press-Centre/Press-releases/2007/Media-contact-line.html?id=450400" title="">
                        Media contact line
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[11.02.2007]</p>
                <p>Beginning on Monday, 12 February, the Ministry of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs will staff a media contact line during working hours. The press must exclusively use the telephone number +47 22 24 66 99 between 8.00 and 15.45 on weekdays.     </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
